data.description: Welcome to this charming single-story home located in the vibrant city of Austin, TX. This home offers 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms, perfect for a growing family or anyone looking for a comfortable living space. Additionally, there is a study room that can be utilized as a home office or a quiet retreat.    Primary bed offers a spacious area for relaxing from your day. Primary bath offers dual vanities, soaking tub and walk in shower and closet.    The layout of the house includes a choice between a formal dining room or a flexible space that can be customized to suit your needs. Enjoy the convenience and open feel as the kitchen seamlessly flows into the living area, creating an ideal space for entertaining friends and family.    The kitchen boasts recently updated non-stainless steel appliances, providing a modern touch while retaining a classic elegance. Fresh carpeting and flooring in the kitchen and laundry area further enhance the overall appeal of this well-maintained home.    Step outside and discover a private and serene backyard, perfect for relaxation and creating lasting memories. Additionally, this home is conveniently located near major highways, ensuring easy access to the surrounding areas. Enjoy the proximity to shopping centers for all your retail needs and the nearby walking trails with parks for those seeking an active lifestyle.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience all that Austin has to offer.
